* Emacs-dotfiles

These are my emacs dotfiles.  They mainly pertain to org-mode 'cause that's
what I mainly use Emacs for.

* Installation:

  - Rename your ~/.emacs.d to a backup folder
  - git clone http://github.com/NathanNeff/emacs-dotfiles.git ~/.emacs.d
  - ln -s ~/.emacs.d/emacs ~/.emacs
  - cd ~/.emacs.d
  - git submodule init
  - git submodule update
  - cd ~/.emacs.d/src/org
  - make
* Refresh / update

  - cd ~/.emacs.d
  - git pull origin master
  - (I don't know if you have to do anything w/submodules) git submodule 
